+- R1-M2 [verify]: addressed in `6911611` — `PhysicsContractPanel` is rendered first inside `StoryTab`, above the explanatory sections, so the reader sees the contract before the downstream PASS/HAZARD/FAIL surface (`ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnCaseDetailPage.tsx:331-339`).
