+- R1-N3 — still present at `61140c4`: the Advanced-tab audit-package bridge drops `case`/`run` context even though the header CTA preserves it; the two paths are inconsistent (`ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnCaseDetailPage.tsx:234-237`, `ui/frontend/src/pages/learn/LearnCaseDetailPage.tsx:1372-1374`).
